****************** Aaru - Your Personal Companion ******************

This is a voice assistant project which is based upon the pythons speech recognition module. It used python libraries such as - 
1. speech_recognition - to recognize speech
3. pyjokes - to tell random jokes
4. pyttsx3 - for text to speech conversion, etc.

The aim of this project is to learn to create different functionalities using speech recognition like 
1. telling jokes, 
2. telling information from wikipedia, 
3. telling weather, 
4. making a todo list, 
5. playing music, 
6. setting reminders, etc.
